The paper discusses the construction of an artificial general intelligence system, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The main thrust of research proposed is the development of a general data compression algorithm, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses grounded reasoning, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and computational cognition (cs.CC).
